after substance abuse and depression, affecting an estimated 19
million Americans. And just as the pharmaceutical industry has
introduced medicines in recent years to alleviate such common
afflictions as obesity, baldness and sexual impotence, it now sees
a huge market in social anxiety. By Anuradha Raghunathan.
