<HEADLINE>
MARINERS IN MIDDLE OF BASEBALL'S FREE AGENCY MESS 
</HEADLINE>
   (Subs for previous; editing changes throughout)  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By LAURA VECSEY  
 c.1999 Seattle Post-Intelligencer  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; rr &LR;
</P>
