<P>
   TEEPEN-COLUMN _ What is scarier than Newt Gingrich in office?
Newt Gingrich out of office. He came roaring back last week in
Washington, with a speech that was red meat to the lionesses of the
Republican Women Leaders Forum. (Tom Teepen is national
correspondent for Cox Newspapers.) MOVED MONDAY.
