   SCHUETT-COLUMN _ GIBSONBURG, Ohio _ When folks tell me how kids
have changed, I listen with a jaundiced ear, because I'm hearing a
lot of the same things I heard from grownups half-a-century ago.
And sometimes I wonder who has really done the changing. Us or
them? (Schuett, Cox News Service) MOVED.
