and guide, ``Helping Teens Make Responsible Choices'' _ emphasizing
ways to prepare young people to say no. It's a reminder that
conservatives and the Christian right do not own the copyright on
abstinence. (Young, Waco Tribune-Herald) MOVED.
</P>
