   WITH: LIVER BOX: A primer on what your liver does. (Includes a
1-column illustration of the body with focus on the liver.)
</P>
<P>
   WITH: HEPATITIS C HELP BOX: Where to turn for information if you
need to know more about Hepatitis C.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: BOYS EMOTIONS: Young boys need to express their emotions
with tears and hugs without being ridiculed, says psychologist
William Pollack, in a new book. (Includes 6-pica color photo of
book jacket.)
</P>
<P>
   WITH: BOOK EXCERPT: For the next few weeks, the SCIENCE &AMP; HEALTH
page will feature excerpts of a book that addresses the conflict
issue, ``Tired of Yelling?'' This week: The first step in resolving
conflict is identifying the source. (Includes 6-pica color photo of
book jacket.)
