   &QL; 
 &QL; 
SAN FRANCISCO _  &UR; SECRETS-Filet &LR;  _ It's a marvelous triad _ beef,
lavender and black pepper. But it took John McReynolds at Cafe La
Haye to bring it to everyone's attention.
</P>
<P>
   With recipe, chef's secrets for success. &QL; 
 &UR; By Michael Bauer &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR; c. 1999 The San Francisco Chronicle &QL;  &LR; 
