<DOCNO> NYT19990518.0199 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-18 17:12 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1921 &Cx1f; tad-z
