<P>
   ISRAEL (Jerusalem) _ Now what? The new parliament could pose
problems for Ehud Barak, the newly elected prime minister, on the
peace effort and cohesion of Israeli society. Barak visited to the
Western Wall and the grave of the assassinated prime minister
Yitzhak Rabin. By Deborah Sontag.
</P>
<P>
   With a photo and a graphic on the composition of the new
parliament.
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-NATO (Brussels) _ Developments on Kosovo from NATO
headquarters. By Michael R. Gordon.
