   &UR;  &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR; BUSINESS &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR;  &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR; PROVIDIAN  &LR; _ The San Francisco DA's office is conducting a criminal
investigation of possible consumer financial fraud by Providian
Financial Corp. The probe will look at a slew of complaints over
such matters as inadequate disclosure of fees, and questionable
collection practices. By Sam Zuckerman
