</P>
<P>
   SEC-DATEK (Undated) _ In one of its first actions against an
online brokerage firm, the Securities and Exchange Commission said
Tuesday that it had sanctioned Datek Online, one of the nation's
fastest-growing online brokers, for filing a false financial report
and dipping into customer money last year, in part to pay off
company expenses. By David Barboza.
</P>
<P>
   (The story is scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET.)
</P>
