</P>
<P>
   MARKET (New York) _ Stock prices were slightly lower Tuesday but
well above their lows of the session, as traders and investors
reacted with relative equanimity to the decision by the Federal
Reserve Board to adopt a more hawkish stance on interest rates. By
Kenneth N. Gilpin.
