   8-8:30 p.m.: ``Spin City''
</P>
<P>
   8:30-9 p.m.: ``It's like, you know ... ''
</P>
<P>
   9-9:30 p.m.: ``Dharma &AMP; Greg''
</P>
<P>
   9:30-10 p.m.: ``Sports Night''
</P>
<P>
   10-11 p.m.: ``NYPD Blue'' (``Once and Again'' prior to ``NYPD
Blue'' season premiere)
</P>
<P>
   WEDNESDAY
</P>
