   TRADE-RAMSEY-COLUMN (Seattle) _ Exports create jobs. How many
times have we heard that? But do imports destroy jobs? If exports
are good, are imports bad?
</P>
<P>
   By Bruce Ramsey. (Story will move in the ``f'' category.)
